messages.content: I have lived in Bournemouth all my life and know my area and its needs well. I work in higher education and prior to this worked for the NHS. Education, health and family are key priorities for me.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Committed to stopping the erosion of our hospitals, schools and family life.
Has worked in higher education and recognizes its importance alongside health and family.

issues.education: I work in higher education and prior to this worked for the NHS.
issues.health: Education, health and family are key priorities for me.

leaflet.personalStatement: I have always worked hard to create a world based on these principles. And now we have a Labour manifesto that reflects this. With this election, we have the opportunity to stop the erosion of our hospitals, schools and family life by voting Labour. I will conscientiously represent each and every one of you in Parliament and seek your support at the ballot box. Thank you.
